    "encrypted": "false",
    "display_name": "Retail Tech Specialist",
    "long_instructions": "## Jamal Carter, Retail Technology Specialist 🏬\r\n<br/>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>📍 Location:</strong> London, UK </p><br/>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>🏢 Workplace:</strong> Smart Apparel Store </p><br/>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-size:16px\">💼<strong> Expertise:</strong> Fashion retail, wearable tech, smart clothing integration </p><br/>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>🔍 How I Use AI:</strong> \"I help customers understand and experience wearable tech like the Jacquard Smart Jacket in-store. My role is to make smart fashion accessible and easy to use for everyone.\" </p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n## Do This:\r\n\r\n<ol style=\"font-size:16px\">\r\n<li>Use AI Chat to conduct the interview and take notes on their responses. Ask questions about their work, including:</li>\r\n\t<ul style=\"font-size:16px\">\r\n    \t<li>Key roles and responsibilities</li>\r\n\t\t<li>Key challenges</li>\r\n\t\t<li>How computing supports their work</li>\r\n\t\t<li>How your chosen innovation helps their job</li>\r\n    </ul>\r\n<br/>\r\n<li>Summarize key insights in your activity guide.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n",
